Employers take advantage of this, particularly big companies such as the ones operating the mine. 
They do not comply with the code and, in any case, do not care about these ridiculous fines. 
They can afford to pay them.  
This is a crucial point and I think it should be entirely reviewed.  
Powers should also be given to these industries' employees. 
